Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.58,0:00:09.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hunt them to extinction!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.54,0:00:14.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those in Lutiel's fleet \Nare now under my command.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.25,0:00:16.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Charge the vanguard!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.80,0:00:28.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am less than amused by \Ntheir assault on the gate.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.96,0:02:19.44,Ep Title,,0000,0000,0000,,"Alea Iacta Est"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.16,0:02:18.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It will take six hours for the \NStraggle Laser to fully recharge.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.75,0:02:21.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll need to devise a \Nplan to tide us over.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.91,0:02:23.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But none of our attacks have been
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.47,0:02:24.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,effective against them in the past.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.34,0:02:29.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maximize the rate of convergence \Nto increase penetration.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.60,0:02:31.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Blue 1's attack has already proven
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.81,0:02:34.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that physical rounds should \Nbe capable of penetrating
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.25,0:02:35.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the high-energy barrier.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.87,0:02:37.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I suggest we take the initiative
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.93,0:02:40.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and hit them with a saturation attack
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.19,0:02:41.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to cripple their defense network and
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.94,0:02:43.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,destroy the gate's control system.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.74,0:02:44.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Permission granted!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.53,0:02:46.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Star Rose and the fleet ships
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.95,0:02:49.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,will launch a controlled \Nartillery attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.49,0:02:53.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Roger. I will link all of our fleet's \Nsublight-speed guided missiles.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.62,0:02:56.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Link established!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.33,0:02:58.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Excellent.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.57,0:03:01.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fire all of our sublight-speed \Nguided missiles!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.67,0:03:08.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The sublight-speed guided missiles have
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.18,0:03:09.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,entered their second stage acceleration.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.93,0:03:11.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Missile impact in 30 seconds!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.56,0:03:16.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All of the sublight-speed guided \Nmissiles have been destroyed!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.27,0:03:23.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is Lumes' unit.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.69,0:03:26.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They have the tightest \Ndefenses amongst the Wulgaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.36,0:03:29.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They destroyed all of those guided \Nmissiles in a split second...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.07,0:03:31.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So a long-range battle has \Nbeen rendered impossible?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.20,0:03:31.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.12,0:03:34.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The 1st and 2nd Area Fleets' \Nrate of attrition is at 45%!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.33,0:03:37.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Bela-Russian and the \NGreat Chinese Alliance's
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.92,0:03:39.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,fleets have begun to pull back.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.38,0:03:40.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All fleets, tighten your formation!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.17,0:03:43.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyone who pulls away from the \Nmain fleet will get picked off!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.67,0:03:45.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But the Straggle Laser and our
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.29,0:03:48.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,saturation attack with sublight \Nguided missiles ended in failure.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.88,0:03:50.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll have to land a direct hit...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.68,0:03:53.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Information on Team \NRabbits... just came in!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.64,0:04:00.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how many I shoot, \Nthere's still more of 'em!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.06,0:04:03.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They have us completely surrounded.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.27,0:04:05.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My ammunition is down to 15%!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.40,0:04:07.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just about outta energy!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.87,0:04:10.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Move it, you lowly insects!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.28,0:04:12.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It makes me sick how you're \Nswarming everywhere!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.24,0:04:14.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Guys...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.61,0:04:18.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you refuse to show yourself,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.29,0:04:21.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will force you to come out of hiding.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.33,0:04:25.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Blue 1's remaining \Nenergy is down to 25%.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.53,0:04:27.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rose 3 is down to 18%.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.84,0:04:29.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It will be difficult for \Nthem to continue fighting.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.17,0:04:32.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have them pull back, restock and refuel.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.51,0:04:35.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the Godinion. \NDo you read, Kitty?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.01,0:04:36.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I repeat, this is the Godinion.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.68,0:04:37.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Meow, I hear ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.06,0:04:39.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All units are to return for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.35,0:04:43.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm confirming the route.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.62,0:04:47.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Retreat through Points 21-AF through EM.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.36,0:04:48.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll transfer the data.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.85,0:04:51.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pull back while I keep 'em busy \Nwith some diversionary shots!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.07,0:04:52.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Roger!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.24,0:04:53.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All units-
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.62,0:04:55.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look out!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.72,0:04:58.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There is a rapidly approaching \Nhigh speed heat source!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.04,0:05:00.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tamaki, run for it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.75,0:05:02.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.38,0:05:09.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's that fighter from way back...!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.84,0:05:14.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's dangerous! Get out \Nof there, Big Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.68,0:05:16.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You heard him, Big Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.51,0:05:19.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Verification on the \Nhostile object: Complete!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.89,0:05:22.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the guy from Ceres!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.98,0:05:25.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's blocking our escape route.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.31,0:05:26.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are there any other routes?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.83,0:05:29.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'd have to cut straight through \Nthe middle of the enemy's fleet.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.61,0:05:30.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This sucks...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.84,0:05:32.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you acting like wusses?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.54,0:05:33.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's just a single fighter!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.95,0:05:36.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure we'll manage somehow \Nif everyone goes after him.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.02,0:05:38.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess that's our only option...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.91,0:05:40.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kei, navigate!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.79,0:05:42.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Suruga, offer backup support!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.47,0:05:43.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Roger!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.71,0:05:45.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tamaki, take the front of the Kette.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.28,0:05:47.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ange, take the support position.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.85,0:05:48.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Roger!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.42,0:05:50.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay! Charge!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.92,0:05:53.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I may have lost my boosters, \Nbut I still have my weapons!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.60,0:05:59.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Leave him to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.18,0:06:04.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's in position!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.60,0:06:08.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He dodged that?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.23,0:06:10.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.92,0:06:11.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not done yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.28,0:06:13.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Big Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.32,0:06:16.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How much energy do they have left?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.82,0:06:19.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Blue 1 is at 1.9%.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.41,0:06:21.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He can't even get back off that...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.66,0:06:23.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Should we send him a booster?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.54,0:06:24.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can we?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.71,0:06:26.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The preparations are already complete,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.08,0:06:28.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but I'm not sure the enemy will \Ngive him enough time to dock...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.21,0:06:30.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are his chances of \Nsuccessfully docking?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.20,0:06:32.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,43.8%.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.55,0:06:35.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It beats doing nothing and watching him
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.08,0:06:36.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,get cut down when he runs out of energy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.98,0:06:37.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Launch it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.93,0:06:38.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Roger!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.89,0:06:43.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Asagi, your booster is \Ncoming. Dock with it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.53,0:06:45.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Roger!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.77,0:06:47.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ange, fill in for me right quick!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.56,0:06:49.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure thing! Suruga, back me up!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.42,0:06:51.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She finally said my name!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.69,0:06:53.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry it up, ya damn bug!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.19,0:06:55.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll help you out!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.23,0:07:06.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Reinforcements!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.37,0:07:10.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To think that I would feel the urge to
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.15,0:07:12.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,immerse myself in the \Nhunt after all this time!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.30,0:07:15.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I never expected Dolgana to \Npersonally enter the fray!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.03,0:07:19.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He is the Wulgaru's greatest general.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.09,0:07:22.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ange!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.43,0:07:25.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.56,0:07:27.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll deal with this bogey!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.04,0:07:38.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My unit's heavy!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.70,0:07:39.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it all to hell!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.53,0:07:45.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Blue 1, you're down \Nto 3% residual energy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.08,0:07:48.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're at risk if you keep fighting!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.42,0:07:53.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cut power to my left arm!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.39,0:07:54.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pull back!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.39,0:07:56.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Until we defeat this guy, \Nthat's not an option!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.05,0:07:59.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are there any surplus forces?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.08,0:07:59.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, ma'am!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.94,0:08:01.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What weapons do we have \Nleft on this vessel?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.19,0:08:04.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just a multipurpose short-range \Nguided missile launcher.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.64,0:08:06.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't have the range you need.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.89,0:08:10.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.95,0:08:16.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But the next time you get in that \NAHSMB unit, it could kill you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.40,0:08:20.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone is out there fighting \Ntheir hardest so you don't have to.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.11,0:08:22.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you going to put \Ntheir efforts to waste?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.32,0:08:24.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That may be true, but I...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.04,0:08:27.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm ordering you to \Nwait in your quarters.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.54,0:08:29.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Peko, escort him.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.82,0:08:30.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain Suzukaze!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.21,0:08:34.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.46,0:08:35.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wha-?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.46,0:08:36.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Reika,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.85,0:08:38.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Siegfried,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.51,0:08:39.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Guiliano,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.92,0:08:40.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Peko,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.18,0:08:42.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Natori Shion,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.05,0:08:44.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Degawa,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.13,0:08:45.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mayu,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.23,0:08:46.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dan,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.51,0:08:48.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,everyone on the pit crew,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.14,0:08:50.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Commander Simon,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.49,0:08:51.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Teoria,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.02,0:08:52.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kei,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.98,0:08:53.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tamaki,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.90,0:08:54.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ange,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.81,0:08:56.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Suruga,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.15,0:08:57.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and my big brother, Asagi,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.28,0:09:00.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I love all of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.15,0:09:03.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was born all by myself,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.13,0:09:04.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,never knowing what my parents look like.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.37,0:09:09.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But now I have a family \Nand I love so many people!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.66,0:09:11.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't die for their sake...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.66,0:09:12.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And besides...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.92,0:09:14.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And besides,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.68,0:09:17.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I still have a bunch of \Nmanga that I want to draw!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.17,0:09:21.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So I'm not going to die!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.93,0:09:23.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Probably...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.01,0:09:25.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Probably," he says.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.47,0:09:28.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it's just like him to fall flat.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.39,0:09:31.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't this when you're supposed \Nto give up and let him go?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.11,0:09:34.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll have to pardon me, but \Nconsidering our current situation,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.40,0:09:36.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I believe it will be difficult to turn
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.32,0:09:38.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the tables without dispatching Red 5.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.36,0:09:41.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go get 'em.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.94,0:09:44.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's easy for you to say!\N His unit is currently locked...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.65,0:09:45.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He can go whenever he's ready!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.70,0:09:47.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all warmed up!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.32,0:09:49.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can take it to full power!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.62,0:09:54.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, then. Red \N5, prepare to sortie.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.54,0:09:56.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'd better come back to us!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.38,0:09:58.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, ma'am!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.64,0:10:13.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Blast off!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.19,0:10:23.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're counting on you...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.36,0:10:25.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you've finally come.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.16,0:10:29.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Izuru?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.91,0:10:31.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dude, what're you doin' here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.90,0:10:34.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We told you to keep out of \Nthis, you freakin' moron!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.44,0:10:35.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You stoopy-poopy head!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.33,0:10:39.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We told you to take it \Neasy and stay on the ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.38,0:10:40.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.79,0:10:43.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After all, I'm the hero... probably.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.55,0:10:45.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's with that, "probably"?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.48,0:10:48.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been eagerly awaiting \Nyour arrival, my lamata!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.30,0:10:50.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Guys, withdraw while you still can!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.48,0:10:55.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Roger...!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.57,0:11:11.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Great Chinese Alliance \Nis currently fleeing!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.91,0:11:14.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bela-Russia is maintaining their \Nbattle formation as they skirt back.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.95,0:11:17.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Africa's forces are in chaos!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.29,0:11:21.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The 1st Area Fleet's frontline \Nrate of attrition is at 64.9%!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.79,0:11:23.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How do things look for the Rabbits?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.21,0:11:24.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll put it on the screen!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.22,0:11:29.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So their hands are tied, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.76,0:11:32.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fire all of the main cannons \Nsimultaneously at Point DN-31!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.97,0:11:35.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,While we're doing that, have \Nthe 1st and 2nd Fleets
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.12,0:11:36.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,retreat at full speed.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.39,0:11:40.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The enemy is quickly closing in on us!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.55,0:11:42.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't care if we burn \Nout all of our cannons!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.59,0:11:44.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fire! Fire! Fire like mad!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.82,0:11:46.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are too many of them!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.28,0:11:49.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Enemy fighters are advancing.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.81,0:11:50.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the situation?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.16,0:11:54.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They'll get to start firing at us \Nlong before they enter our range.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.79,0:11:56.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is bad... Can you handle this?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.90,0:11:58.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please leave everything to us!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.25,0:12:00.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My dream is to lead a carefree \Nlife living off pension,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.60,0:12:02.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so I'll push myself a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.31,0:12:04.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sending you all of the enemy's \Nverified locations and past maneuvers.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.13,0:12:08.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Roger. After calculating their \Nanticipated movement patterns,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.17,0:12:10.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to pull out everything \Nfrom the top to 1024.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.80,0:12:13.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Inputting random firing coefficients \Nfor the anticipated patterns.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.97,0:12:15.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've indicated that the ship \Nis to prioritize safety
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.53,0:12:17.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,while also eliminating \Nany margin of error.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.47,0:12:19.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we drop the safety margin by 0.2,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.71,0:12:22.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the evasion rate goes up 14.72%.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.91,0:12:24.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How would that affect the safety?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.27,0:12:26.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm guessing we'll lose \Nour kitchen plates
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.05,0:12:28.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and suffer muscle pain in the morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.46,0:12:29.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.57,0:12:32.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Roger! I'm sending over \Nthe pilot control data.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.36,0:12:34.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our vessel will begin \Ntaking evasive measures!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.95,0:12:37.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All crew, you have 20 \Nseconds to brace yourselves
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.43,0:12:39.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and prepare for turbulence!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.08,0:12:41.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're down to 10 seconds!\N Pilot controls are set for full auto!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.18,0:12:44.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Five,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.63,0:12:45.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,four,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.92,0:12:46.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,three,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.30,0:12:48.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,two,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.84,0:12:49.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,one!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.22,0:12:50.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Accelerate!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.56,0:12:59.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The evasive pattern is \Nwithin permissible range!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.73,0:13:03.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a good thing they're drawing the \Nbig shots' attention away from us.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.40,0:13:05.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fire all weapons!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.67,0:13:14.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's faster than before!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.74,0:13:18.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I don't stop him here and now...!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.12,0:13:23.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Crap!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.84,0:13:27.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.05,0:13:33.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just now...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.33,0:13:39.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please send me fuel, ammunition, \Na left arm and a booster pod!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.22,0:13:40.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're ready to go!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.72,0:13:42.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just gotta input your coordinates.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.35,0:13:44.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I should have known. \NPlease send them over.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.68,0:13:47.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Knowing you, don't freak out \Nand screw up the docking.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.90,0:13:49.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Change the parts, quick!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.56,0:13:51.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're all out of spare boosters.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.28,0:13:52.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now what?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.28,0:13:54.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't care what you \Ndo, just do something!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.58,0:14:01.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now I remember...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.71,0:14:10.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.19,0:14:12.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I shouldn't suppress the \NAHSMB's survival instinct...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.09,0:14:18.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rather than defy its survival instinct,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.68,0:14:20.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I should provide it directionality!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.47,0:14:22.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.78,0:14:24.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me see more of what you can do!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.77,0:14:27.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're just a stinking big bug!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.40,0:14:28.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The way you keep scurrying \Nhere and there,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.74,0:14:30.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you must be a cockroach!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.77,0:14:32.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me squish you already!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.19,0:14:35.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it! Why can't I hit him?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.24,0:14:39.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Escort vessel Takanami, destroyed.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.74,0:14:42.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Close-Support Fleet down to 21 ships!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.61,0:14:44.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our vessel's firing capabilities \Nare down to 12%.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.75,0:14:48.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've lost our armor plating \Nfrom Block 1 to Block 3.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.13,0:14:50.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The engine is still capable \Nof working at maximum power!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.50,0:14:52.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It will take another \Neight minutes for the
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.43,0:14:53.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,1st and 2nd Fleets to reorganize.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.80,0:14:55.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Great Chinese Alliance \Nand Bela-Russian's army
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.80,0:14:57.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,are out of our sensor's range.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.26,0:14:59.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How long before the Straggle \NLaser is fully charged?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.35,0:15:01.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It will be ready in ten minutes!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.59,0:15:03.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter what the cost,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.22,0:15:05.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we must destroy that \Ngate's control system!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.06,0:15:07.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Engine at full power!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.44,0:15:09.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have the remaining fleets \Nenter Code: Fish Formation!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.52,0:15:11.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Prepare to charge!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.19,0:15:16.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our ship will now break through the \Ncenter of the enemy's formation...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.15,0:15:18.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and head for the gate!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.07,0:15:21.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tally-ho!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.49,0:15:22.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The cavalry has arrived!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.29,0:15:24.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Doberman...?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.66,0:15:26.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm part of Doberman 2 now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.87,0:15:28.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All units, charge!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.39,0:15:33.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those are the mass-produced AHSMB units!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.76,0:15:37.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The enemy vanguard is pulling back!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.16,0:15:43.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Retrieving those units made us run late.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.88,0:15:47.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pulling back to lure the enemy in \Nis a traditional tactic of ours.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.43,0:15:49.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now is the time for a counterattack!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.12,0:15:52.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There is nowhere for \Nus to go but forward!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.25,0:15:55.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The 1st and 2nd Fleets \Nhave finished regrouping!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.03,0:15:56.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All fleets, advance!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.56,0:15:58.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We will seize the gate \Nin one fell swoop!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.86,0:16:00.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Remaining distance: 20%.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.55,0:16:02.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The gate is within firing range!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.83,0:16:04.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All ships, concentrate \Nyour fire on the gate!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.74,0:16:06.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hit it with everything you've got!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.20,0:16:09.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All units, open your \Nfields to maximum output.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.84,0:16:16.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Clear them out.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.80,0:16:18.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They blocked our attack?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.42,0:16:19.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here comes the counterattack!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.80,0:16:21.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Enter shock-absorbing \Ndefensive positions!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.39,0:16:24.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damage report!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.31,0:16:27.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go! Go! Go! Go! Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.77,0:16:31.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not done yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.73,0:16:38.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Big Brother and Teoria...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.24,0:16:40.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give me the power to protect everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.61,0:16:43.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Izuru Hitachi's Harmonic \NLevel is rising.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.42,0:16:46.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Red 5 has reached maximum output.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.71,0:16:53.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Contacting Rada and Klein's squad.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.08,0:16:55.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Prepare to fire at full power.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.77,0:16:57.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Annihilate the enemy \Nwith that one attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.05,0:17:00.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Forces have decreased by 21%.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.55,0:17:02.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've lost our armor \Nplating up to Block 5!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.01,0:17:05.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's dangerous to continue \Nparticipation in the battle!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.41,0:17:07.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But we can't afford to stop now!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.81,0:17:08.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Enemy reinforcements!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.35,0:17:14.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How much longer before we \Ncan fire the Straggle Laser?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.17,0:17:15.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Five minutes!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.52,0:17:16.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're running out of time!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.23,0:17:20.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll ram our ship into \Nthe gate's control system.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.53,0:17:23.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All crew, prepare to abandon ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.11,0:17:24.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold off on that!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.82,0:17:26.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll hit it with this!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.12,0:17:29.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But how?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.29,0:17:32.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ta-da-da!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.12,0:17:34.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for waiting!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.05,0:17:45.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Klein's squad, attack \Nthe enemy vanguard.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.59,0:17:47.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rada's squad, serve as mobile \Ndefense on the flanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.14,0:17:49.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't let them through!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.93,0:17:52.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Straggle Laser will be \Nready to fire in two minutes!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.82,0:17:59.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you all right, Asagi?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.57,0:18:01.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Yeah, this is nothing,"
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.36,0:18:04.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...or so I'd like to say, but \Nthere are too many of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.00,0:18:10.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It can't be...!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.55,0:18:20.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Something just came out!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.88,0:18:22.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a new model!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.36,0:18:25.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,People of Wulgaru, listen to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.63,0:18:26.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My name is...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.39,0:18:30.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My name is Pleguzesia Teoria.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.72,0:18:34.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am a descendant of the great Dakihaan
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.64,0:18:36.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,as well as one who shares the
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.51,0:18:39.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,genes of the rightful ruler \Nof the galaxy, Eguzes Galkie.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.57,0:18:42.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those who hear my voice,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.03,0:18:45.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pleguzesia Teoria orders you:
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.45,0:18:47.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Retreat immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.53,0:18:48.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Teoria?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.37,0:18:50.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's pretty...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.87,0:18:52.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's like a goddess.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.41,0:18:54.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't try to flirt with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.33,0:18:55.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She waited for the best possible timing!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.92,0:18:57.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You knew about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.79,0:18:59.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You should have shown yourself sooner!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.42,0:19:05.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Teoria?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.63,0:19:06.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Teoria!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.26,0:19:09.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not happening!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.72,0:19:11.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I swear I will protect Teoria!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.81,0:19:20.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I never expected that I \Nwould take you seriously...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.86,0:19:23.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hear the throbbing pulse of my genes!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.15,0:19:27.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like I'm gonna let you get away!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.53,0:19:30.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it! You're a lame coward the \Nway you're so freaking quick to run!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.99,0:19:34.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a pity!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.06,0:19:37.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You shoulda gotten \Nhere sooner, slowpoke!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.83,0:19:39.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're going to hit him from both sides.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.24,0:19:41.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stay out of my line of fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.46,0:19:42.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't order me around!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.62,0:19:50.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are doing this of your \Nown free will, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.63,0:19:58.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's goin' on?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.02,0:20:01.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A path to our goal just opened up.\N Charge full speed ahead!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.72,0:20:03.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Roger that!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.43,0:20:06.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?!\NEveryone, return to your posts!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.57,0:20:10.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're up against me!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.26,0:20:13.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't forget about me! \NStay in formation.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.06,0:20:16.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I already told you, \Ndon't order me around!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.20,0:20:18.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Release the final safety lock.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.96,0:20:20.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rate of convergence: 500.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.71,0:20:27.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.07,0:20:29.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm counting on you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.22,0:20:30.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tamaki, come back!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.30,0:20:32.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Roger!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.22,0:20:39.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nine, eight, seven,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.14,0:20:43.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,six, five, four,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.88,0:20:46.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,three, two!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.32,0:20:50.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.70,0:20:52.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fire the Straggle Laser!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.67,0:21:08.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Will this do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.30,0:21:12.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Straggle Laser has been hit!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.10,0:21:16.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that... Dolgana's unit?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.64,0:21:20.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Straggle Laser has \Nbeen completely destroyed.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.44,0:21:24.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've... run out of options.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.56,0:21:27.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, we still have one left.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.37,0:21:36.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's completely awoken...?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.83,0:21:40.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The awakened Red 5 will \Nilluminate the path.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.62,0:21:43.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We will hit the gate with the largest \Nbody of mobile mass we have.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.87,0:21:45.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Roger!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.71,0:21:47.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All crew, quickly abandon \Nthe ship from both sides-
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.34,0:21:48.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Amane's ship is to stay as it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.30,0:21:53.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Star Rose's crew is to \Nabandon ship on the double!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.84,0:21:56.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to ram the \NStar Rose into the gate.
